==Description==

<div class="mw-translate-fuzzy">
Extrae la parte común (intersección) entre los objetos piezas seleccionados. Esta operación es completamente paramétrica y los componentes pueden ser modificados y el resultado recalculado.
</div>

== Usage ==

# Select two shapes
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:Part_Common.svg|16px]] [[Part_Common|Common]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Part → Boolean → [[Image:Part_Common.svg|16px]] Common}} option from the menu.

== Supported inputs ==

Input objects must be [[OpenCASCADE|OpenCASCADE]] shapes. Examples: stuff made with Part, PartDesign, Sketcher workbenches. Not meshes (unless those were converted to shapes) - for meshes, there are specific Boolean tools in MeshDesign workbench.


